To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private MassIndex _mass;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_mass = MASS(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_mass.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "massindex", _mass.Current.Value);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.mass = self.MASS(symbol)

# In OnData()
if self.mass.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "massindex", self.mass.Current.Value)
